Egypt Intensifies Search for Extremists in Sinai, Masry Reports

-- B y   O l a   G a l a l
-- 
2011-08-30T09:17:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-30/egypt-intensifies-search-for-extremists-in-sinai-masry-reports.html
Egyptian troops and security forces
have intensified searches in Sinai for extremists as the
authorities heightened the state of emergency over the
peninsula,  Al Masry Al Youm  reported, citing unidentified
security sources.  The troops, numbering 1,500 and backed by tanks and armored
vehicles, stepped up the raids around the cities of Rafah, El-
Arish and Sheikh Zoweid, the Cairo-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ola Galal at 
 ogalal@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Stephen Voss  on   sev@bloomberg.net . 